Experienced Salesforce Developer with over 4 years of hands-on expertise in architecting and delivering scalable solutions across Sales Cloud, Service Cloud, B2B Commerce, and Experience Cloud. Skilled in full-stack Salesforce development using Lightning Web Components (LWC), Aura, Visualforce, Apex, Triggers, and asynchronous Apex. Proven ability in integrating Salesforce with external systems using REST/SOAP APIs and ConnectAPI, including secure payment processing with CyberSource and shipping/logistics integration with FedEx and UPS. Adept in DevOps practices and Salesforce ALM, leveraging Git, Bitbucket, Salesforce DX, and Flosum to streamline CI/CD pipelines. Recognized for improving order management workflows, optimizing UI responsiveness, and enhancing system reliability through performance tuning and data handling best practices. Holds multiple Salesforce certifications and consistently delivers business-focused solutions aligned with industry standards and client expectations.
